  "body": "# Problem\nWhen currency conversion error is shown, snackbar obtrudes content, specifically total asset value.\n\n## Current behavior\nSnackbar overlays wallet content\n\n## Exected behavior\nSnackbar pushes wallet content down\n\n![signal-2019-03-01-080741](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35233054/53635884-cb5bfe80-3c1e-11e9-93bf-85b15b96c07f.png)\n\n\n# Implementation\nIn Chat a new Snackbar component was implemented that pushes content down, rather than be displayed as an overlay.\n\n# Acceptance Criteria\nOn all occasions snackbar is shown in wallet, wallet content is pushed down.\nRules for the future PR to be accepted.\n\n\n# Future Steps\nCheck for other places where older version of snackbar is used.",
