    "body": "@hesterbruikman This was actually intentional. The thing that gets hidden away is the total asset value *in fiat*. Now, this error happens when conversion rates are unknown because the api that gives us the rates is unreachable, e.g. blocked by proxy, down or phone is simply offline. \r\n\r\nIn that case, we were previously displaying 0, which is misleading and outright scary. At some point we made it hide the figure in this scenario, as its fiat value is meaningless without a correct rate.",
